products.title: Macrame Wine Tote
products.description: Searching for the perfect hostess gift? Look no further! Spice up your timeless gift of wine by presenting it in a one-of-kind macrame wine tote. The perfect combination of chic & useful! It can hold any typical-sized wine bottle. Bring one along for a picnic or wine-tasting--you're guaranteed compliments. Grab a few to keep on hand for a lovely housewarming or birthday gift! Comes in natural, faded indigo, mustard, or dusty blush.
